<h2>About </h2>
<p>Welcome to the Short Exact Guide, your definitive source for discriminating reviews of the dizzying array of restaurants found in the San Francisco Bay Area. For your convenience, the categories located at the far right have been divided into cuisines and neighborhoods, so that you can more easily find a restaurant you&#8217;re looking for, or you could use the search tool at the top right of the page.</p>
<p>Is there a restaurant you&#8217;d like to see here that doesn&#8217;t have a review yet? Any culinary stories you&#8217;d like to share? Ideas, comments, suggestions? Please, <a href="mailto:galoisgroupie@gmail.com">don&#8217;t be a stranger</a>.</p>
<p>We hope that you enjoy perusing the reviews. Come back soon and often!
</p>
